title: The Chieftains - The Long Black Veil
description:
The Chieftans - The Long Black Veil - 1995

I love this cd.  It's almost like a 60s rock star reunion celtic style with a few 'newer' voices thrown into the mix.  What can you say when Marianne Faithfull, Mick Jagger, Van Morrisson, Tom Jones, Sinead O'Connor plus others, get together with the legendary Chieftains?  WOW!!!  is what I say.

Ripped to flac from the disc using EAC.  Covers, cue sheet, and playlist are included.
